# Ignore training/eval artifacts in output/ except the metadata of the
# active router checkpoint — it is the single source of truth that the
# docs-check CI validates against the EU AI Act transparency doc. The
# 442 KB router.safetensors stays ignored (derivable from training corpus).
output/*
!output/router-v7-multimodel/
output/router-v7-multimodel/*
!output/router-v7-multimodel/meta.json
!output/router-v7-multimodel/label_map.json
data/
.env
